===Etymology===
From {{etyl|grc}} {{term|ὀνοματοποιία|sc=polytonic|tr=onomatopoiia||the coining of a word in imitation of a sound|lang=grc}}, from {{term|ονοματοποιέω|sc=polytonic|tr=onomatopoieo||to coin names|lang=grc}}, from {{term|ὄνομα|sc=polytonic|tr=onoma||name|lang=grc}} + {{term|ποιέω|sc=polytonic|tr=poieo||to make, to do, to produce|lang=grc}}.

